\begin_inset Formula \( I_{0}=B_{\nu}\left(T_{\mathrm{ring}}\right)\)
\end_inset 

 where 
\begin_inset Formula \( B_{\nu}\)
\end_inset 

 is the Planck function and 
\begin_inset Formula \( T_{\mathrm{ring}}\)
\end_inset 

